    <note x="559" y="933" backgroundDark="0" fontSize="10" width="566" markdown="false" height="40" textColorDark="-1" textColorLight="-5825686" backgroundLight="0">Proxemics is represented as "meeting spaces" people can move into and be infected or spread infection.
